# Single-line, base64-encoded *public* half of the repo signing key.
# Generate/export it with:
#   gpg --export "ProjectNotes Flatpak Signing" | base64 --wrap=0
# Paste the output as the value below (no line breaks). The matching private
# key is held only as the FLATPAK_GPG_PRIVATE_KEY GitHub Actions secret.

